<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I can confirm that </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">your direct debit schedule has XX payments of £00.00 remaining</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>These payments will continue to be taken in accordance with the agreed schedule. Alternatively, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">if you would prefer to pay the remaining balance in full, minus the Direct Debit interest charges, we can process a card payment over the phone</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>As of today, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">the total amount left to pay is £000.00</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, however, this amount will change daily as per the interest on the Direct Debit account.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please let us know how you would like to proceed.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>